          <h2>Responsive tables</h2>
          <p>Create responsive tables by adding
            <font color="red">.table-responsive</font> to any
            <font color="red">&lt;table&gt;</font> to make them stack horizontally on small devices (under 768px). When viewing on anything larger
            than 768px wide, you will not see any difference in these tables.</p>
          <p>If
            <font color="red">&lt;th&gt;</font> is used within
            <font color="red">&lt;tbody&gt;</font> and within
            <font color="red">&lt;tr&gt;</font>, it will remain as a table cell.


            <!-- The data of the
						<font color="red">&lt;th&gt;</font>'s within
						<font color="red">&lt;thead&gt;</font>
						will be appended to the beginning of the relevant 
						<font color="red">&lt;td&gt;</font>.</p>-->


